    <section id="characters">
      <h2>Character Bios</h2>
      <div class="character-grid">
        <article class="character-bio" onmouseover="showFullBio('gresham-full-bio')" onmouseout="hideFullBio('gresham-full-bio')">
          <img src="images/LordGresham.png" alt="Lord Gresham">
          <div class="bio-summary">
            <h3>Lord Gresham</h3>
            <p>Lord Gresham, one of The FEW, commands awe and fear throughout the galaxy.</p>
          </div>
          <div id="gresham-full-bio" class="full-bio">
            <p> He is a formidable figure With dark hair and ocean-blue eyes that turn black during intense emotions. His all-black uniform, devoid of decoration, features the glowing emblem of The FEW, and his dark red cape mirrors his emotional state, billowing and snapping without wind.</p>
            <p>At his side, he carries a sword inscribed with ancient runes that glow ominously, capable of acting as both weapon and shield. Though not an officer, he works closely with the Galactic Alliance, who are honored by his presence. The FEW, a group so rare that many never encounter them, wield immense power, capable of manipulating the atmosphere and creating weather phenomena with ease.</p>
            <p>Lord Gresham’s strategic mind and unyielding will have led his people through countless trials. Despite his stoic exterior, he found an unexpected friend in Commander Alexander Levi. Modeled after a knight, Gresham is dedicated to eradicating evil and maintaining order in the galaxy.</p>
            <p><strong>Quotes and Anecdotes:</strong></p>
            <blockquote>
              <p>"Lord Gresham is an outstanding asset for the Galactic Alliance! As you see, the raiders were captured with only small injuries to the populace. All in all, a program highly executed with precision." – Admiral Yates</p>
            </blockquote>
            <blockquote>
              <p>"Lord Gresham even knew about our situation... He took out the bad guys and saved my family!" – Grateful Father</p>
            </blockquote>
            <blockquote>
              <p>"He is striking to look at. That black uniform, his... aura... that glowing sword at his side, and that swirling cape! Mmmm... pleasing to look at!" – Corporate Executive</p>
            </blockquote>
            <blockquote>
              <p>Bashfully, a First Lieutenant relates one of his first battle experiences on the Requiem: "We were in the thick of battle, and one of the weapons arrays was down. I had sweat pouring off my brow like a water fountain. I got down on the floor and opened the panel, and the smoke made my eyes water, and my palms were sweaty, you know? There I was, and the cables were frayed or burned! I reached out to grab the welder, which slipped and fell on the floor. I was so tense, I could have fried an egg on my chest! Then I hear the staccato of boots, and I KNOW who is standing above me! He gets down on his knees, lays a hand on my arm, and just closes those intense blue eyes. I feel so calm. Like a bright sunny day! I was in the dark and stressed, and then BAM! Cool breezes, sun in my hair, and a beer-in-hand feeling! When I blinked, the welder was in my hand, and I was ready to work!"</p>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="character-bio" onmouseover="showFullBio('mara-full-bio')" onmouseout="hideFullBio('mara-full-bio')">
          <img src="images/LadyMara.png" alt="Lady Mara">
          <div class="bio-summary">
            <h3>Lady Mara</h3>
            <p>Lady Mara, with her lush blonde hair and violet eyes that darken with emotion, is a diplomatic force within The FEW.</p>
          </div>
          <div id="mara-full-bio" class="full-bio">
            <p>She wears the same all-black uniform with the glowing emblem, and her dark red cape reacts to her feelings. Her blue-glowing sword with ancient runes symbolizes her power and authority.</p>
            <p>Mara is known for her compassionate and empathetic nature, often using her words to resolve conflicts. However, she is fierce in pursuing justice and the greater good. Her relationship with Lord Gresham is one of deep loyalty and complex emotions, embodying the balance between fire and water within The FEW.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="character-bio" onmouseover="showFullBio('levi-full-bio')" onmouseout="hideFullBio('levi-full-bio')">
          <img src="images/CommanderLevi.png" alt="Commander Levi">
          <div class="bio-summary">
            <h3>Commander Levi</h3>
            <p>Commander Alexander Levi, known for his unwavering moral compass and strength of character, stands as a beacon of hope and justice within the Galactic Alliance.</p>
          </div>
          <div id="levi-full-bio" class="full-bio">
            <p>Modeled after the heroic ideals of Captain America, Levi is both kind and committed, embodying a rare blend of empathy and determination. Levi’s leadership is marked by his ability to work seamlessly with anyone, fostering a sense of camaraderie and mutual respect among his team. His strategic mind allows him to assess situations quickly and adapt as needed, ensuring the best possible outcomes for both individuals and the larger society.</p>
            <p>He is deeply committed to protecting the rights and freedoms of all beings, standing up for both the one and the many. Whether in the heat of battle or in the quiet moments of diplomacy, Levi’s presence is a source of strength and reassurance to those around him. His heroism and unwavering dedication to justice make him a key ally in the fight against the encroaching darkness.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
